```plantuml
@startuml aws-solutions_automated-security-response-on-aws

actor "Security Analyst" as user
participant "AWS Security Hub" as security_hub
participant "Amazon EventBridge" as event_bridge
participant "Step Functions\n(Orchestrator)" as orchestrator
participant "AWS Systems Manager\n(SSM Automation)" as ssm
participant "AWS Lambda" as lambda
participant "AWS CloudWatch" as cloudwatch
participant "External Ticketing\n(Jira/ServiceNow)" as ticketing

== Security Finding Detection ==
security_hub -> security_hub : Detects security finding
security_hub -> event_bridge : Emits finding event

== Remediation Initiation ==
event_bridge -> orchestrator : Triggers workflow\nwith finding details

== Playbook Selection ==
orchestrator -> lambda : Get remediation playbook\n(Standard/Control ID)
lambda -> orchestrator : Returns playbook reference

== SSM Automation Execution ==
orchestrator -> ssm : Executes remediation runbook
ssm -> lambda : Calls remediation function
lambda -> ssm : Returns remediation result

== Status Update ==
ssm -> orchestrator : Reports remediation status
orchestrator -> security_hub : Updates finding status

== Monitoring & Ticketing ==
orchestrator -> cloudwatch : Logs metrics and events
orchestrator -> ticketing : Creates ticket (if configured)

== User Interaction ==
user -> security_hub : Triggers custom action
security_hub -> event_bridge : Custom action event
event_bridge -> orchestrator : Triggers manual remediation

@enduml
```